title: Round up (A)
creator_credit: Rima Tamou, Pauline Clague and Core Original Productions
brief_description: Two country boys, one white and the other aboriginal find themselves out of place in the hustle and bustle of the big city. What they learn on the journey that they embark upon through unfamiliar territory, is that they are not as different as they first thought.
